  <name>Logisim-ita</name>
  <summary>Educational tool for designing and simulating digital logic circuits</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Logisim-ita is an educational tool for designing and simulating digital logic circuits.
      It provides an intuitive graphical interface for creating complex digital systems
      using basic logic gates, flip-flops, and other digital components.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Drag-and-drop circuit design</li>
      <li>Real-time circuit simulation</li>
      <li>Extensive library of digital components</li>
      <li>Hierarchical circuit design</li>
      <li>Educational resources and examples</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
